// Adjustable dimensions for different bed sizes

/* Standard Bed Dimensions in mm
   Twin:  99 x 190 cm (39 x 75 inches)
   Full:  137 x 190 cm (54 x 75 inches)
   Queen: 152 x 203 cm (60 x 80 inches)
   King:  193 x 203 cm (76 x 80 inches)
